snippet.title: Pikmin 4: Planet Remix Mod - Coming Soon
snippet.description:
This is a Pikmin 4 Mod made by me! The hope for this project is to revamp the entirety of PNF-404. and make Pikmin 4 feel like a new experience again!

Shoutouts: @ProdigiousSP @Raggins @gunnadahun
